                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The code:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;@TailRecursive
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;private&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; BigInteger iterate(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; BigInteger i, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; BigInteger a, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; BigInteger b) {
    i &amp;lt; 1 ? a : iterate(i - 1, b, a + b)
  }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;compiles and works fine with the @TailRecursive commented out. With it in place:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;org.codehaus.groovy.control.MultipleCompilationErrorsException: startup failed:
file:/home/users/russel/Progs/Applications/Fibonacci/Groovy/Fibonacci.groovy: 43: Apparent variable &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;__b__&apos;&lt;/span&gt; was found in a &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; scope but doesn&apos;t refer to a local variable, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; field or class. Possible causes:
You attempted to reference a variable in the binding or an instance variable from a &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; context.
